cattywampus (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging (Fixes #30)
  * Add standard Debian package workflow
  * Support for installation via apt/dpkg
  * Package installs binary to /usr/bin and is available in PATH
  * Automatic user configuration setup on installation
  * File manager integration support
  * External dependencies properly declared (mkvtoolnix, atomicparsley)

